    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a fantastic option for anyone who values functionality and character! It has been a dependable companion and is ready to hit the road with its next owner. While it shows some honest wear from its years of service, it remains a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left!",
