    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a dedicated project car or a source for spare parts. While the engine does turn over, it requires extensive mechanical work, including a suspected head gasket failure and a transmission that slips significantly. The body has noticeable rust and several dents, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is being sold strictly as-is, and towing is advised for transport.",
